            <a class='permalink column-permalink' id='column_214' title='Col. 214 &mdash; Deb 01 August 1924 vol 59 c214' name='column_214' href='#column_214' rel='bookmark'>214</a>
            convinced that it would be best to leave the matter in their hands, as their area goes right outside the area of the London County Council, and because they will be dealing particularly with subjects with which they are competent to deal, such as shipping. I beg to move.
          </p>
